    她是岛上最好的厨师，对美馔佳肴有很深的爱好。

[02:08.47]From morning till night you saw her sitting on a low chair in the kitchen, surrounded by a Chinese cook and two or three native girls,  giving her orders, chatting sociably with all and sundry, and tasting the savoury messes she devised. 
