[02:46.97]When the Chinese laundryman refused to wash for him without payment she had sent his things to be washed with hers.  She could not allow the poor fellow to go about in a dirty shirt, she said, and since he was a man, and men must smoke, she gave him a franc a day for cigarettes. 
